snippet.title: Redemption's Guild Update #5! Vohril's Stand
snippet.description:
In this video we showcase the adventure zone Vohril's Stand.

Early alpha footage - does not represent the final product.

This footage was recorded on an HTC Vive - gameplay and graphics may vary depending on your Headset and hardware.

Online RPG Redemption's Guild - For Oculus Rift and HTC Vive.
